If you have always wondered what the hollow spoon/straw that comes with the McFlurry ice cream is actually used for you are going to be very disappointed. It turns out the square end is there for another far more practical reason many of us had never considered. A McDonald's employee uploaded a video to TikTok, which has been viewed up to more than 3.8 million times, to finally put an end to the debate.User @Marzpire shared a video asking: "Ever wondered why you can't drink out of a McFlurry spoon?"  